#. <section class="sutta" id="sn54.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn54.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 54"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 54"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn54.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn54.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Paṭhamabhikkhusutta"
msgstr "15. Several Mendicants (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.335"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.15:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te "
"bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn54.15:1.2"
msgid ""
"“atthi nu kho, bhante, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, is there one thing that, when developed and cultivated, fulfills four "
"things; and those four things, when developed and cultivated, fulfill seven "
"things; and those seven things, when developed and cultivated, fulfill two "
"things?”"

msgctxt "sn54.15:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Atthi kho, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr "“There is, mendicants.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.15:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Katamo pana, bhante, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro dhamme "
"paripūreti, cattāro dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta dhamme paripūrenti, "
"satta dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā dve dhamme paripūrentī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, what is that one thing?”"

msgctxt "sn54.15:2.2"
msgid ""
"“Ānāpānassatisamādhi kho, bhikkhave, ekadhammo bhāvito bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti, cattāro satipaṭṭhānā bhāvitā bahulīkatā satta "
"bojjhaṅge paripūrenti, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrentīti."
msgstr ""
"“Immersion due to mindfulness of breathing is one thing that, when developed "
"and cultivated, fulfills the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. And the "
"four kinds of mindfulness meditation, when developed and cultivated, fulfill "
"the seven awakening factors. And the seven awakening factors, when developed "
"and cultivated, fulfill knowledge and freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn54.15:3.1"
msgid ""
"Kathaṃ bhāvito ca, bhikkhave, ānāpānassatisamādhi kathaṃ bahulīkato cattāro "
"satipaṭṭhāne paripūreti?"
msgstr ""
"And how is mindfulness of breathing developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill the four kinds of mindfulness meditation? …"

msgctxt "sn54.15:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu araññagato vā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn54.15:3.3"
msgid ""
"evaṃ bhāvitā kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā evaṃ bahulīkatā vijjāvimuttiṃ "
"paripūrentī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how the seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated so as to "
"fulfill knowledge and freedom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn54.15:3.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
